{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"670","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"上市櫃去年營收創10年次高 金管會點名這6產業獲利出色","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>2020-04-07 20:41</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82%E6%AB%83%E7%87%9F%E6%94%B6.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 569px;' />&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>上市去年營收為<span lang='EN-US'>31</span>兆<span lang='EN-US'>8,660</span>億元，上櫃營收為<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>兆<span lang='EN-US'>1,431</span>億元，雙雙創下近十年次高！圖為證期局副局長蔡麗玲。（資料照／記者王孟倫攝）</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>〔記者王孟倫／台北報導〕依規定，上市櫃公司應於三月底申報去年度財報。金管會今天公布上市櫃公司<span lang='EN-US'>2019</span>年度營收及獲利狀況。其中，上市公司去年營業收入<span lang='EN-US'>31</span>兆<span lang='EN-US'>8,660</span>億元，上櫃公司營收為<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>兆<span lang='EN-US'>1,431</span>億元，雙雙創下「近十年次高紀錄」。</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>金管會並點名，上市公司去年有三大產業獲利成長、表現出色，包括：金融保險業、水泥工業及電機機械業，上櫃公司也有三大產業包括：光電業、半導體業及電子商務業。</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>金管會證期局表示，<span lang='EN-US'>2019</span>年上市營收金額為近<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>年次高，不過，因前年為近<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>年最高，基期墊高，故較前年減少<span lang='EN-US'>2,134</span>億元，減少<span lang='EN-US'>0.67%</span>、</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>上市公司去年稅前淨利為<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>兆<span lang='EN-US'>3,032</span>億元，獲利金額居近<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>年第<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>高，亦因前年基期較高，故較前年減少<span lang='EN-US'>2,778</span>億元，減少<span lang='EN-US'>10.76%</span>。</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>證期局指出，去年度上市公司獲利成長包括：金融保險業因淨利息收益、保費收入增加及匯率避險操作得宜而推升獲利；電機機械業因部分公司之虧損子公司停止營運，致集團虧損減少；水泥工業則因需求及價格皆大幅成長而增加獲利。</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>其次，上櫃公司去年度累計營收<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>兆<span lang='EN-US'>1,431</span>億元，營收金額為近<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>年次高，惟因前年為近<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>年最高，基期墊高，故較前年減少<span lang='EN-US'>294</span>億元，減少<span lang='EN-US'>1.35%</span>。</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>上櫃公司去年稅前淨利為<span lang='EN-US'>1,800</span>億元，獲利金額居近<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>年次高，亦因前年基期較高，故較前年減少<span lang='EN-US'>35</span>億元，減少<span lang='EN-US'>1.91%</span>。</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3126132</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-04-08","clk_count":"233"}},"__N_SSG":true}